      "span_text": "Another example of a middle-meiotic (Ndt80-inducible) mRNA that is translationally regulated is CLB3, which is translationally repressed until the initiation of MII  .  demonstrated that an RNA-binding protein, Rim4, translationally represses CLB3 mRNA until MII and that Ime2 down-regulates Rim4 to permit Clb3 translation."
